    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it really does feel like that. like i'm just a passenger in a body that doesn't belong to me anymore. if the person everyone knew is already dead, then what's the point of keeping this physical part around just to suffer through the shame? it feels so heavy and unnecessary.",
